snippet.title: Wanderer - The Fragments of Fate - Announce Trailer | PS VR2 Games
snippet.description:
Embark on a groundbreaking time travel adventure, completely re-imagined for the next generation of VR. Experience history like never before as you step back in time to rewrite the events of the past and reshape the future. 

Wanderer - The Fragments of Fate, is a remake of the award winning, critically acclaimed VR time travel adventure game - Wanderer. 

#ps5 #psvr2 #psvr2games #adventure #timetravel #action #history #historicalmoments
